data.description: Seller offering 1% of list purchase price to Buy Down interest rate! Premier Location! Huge Culdesac Elevated Lot! TRUE attached Next Gen/Casita with private exterior & garage entrance, kitchen, laundry, full bath & bedroom has sliders to backyard. The Grand Entrance has soaring ceilings & tons of light. Kitchen is a culinary dream w/a large island, quartz counters, walk-in pantry & top-of-the-line appliances. Great room has ultimate indoor/outdoor living transition w/stackable sliders. RARE Oversized backyard with 15' Michael Phelps Swim-Spa, Luxury Gazebo, Play gym, irrigated garden & covered patio. The true livable elevated Gazebo has lighting, commercial heater, cool misters & spectacular views. Breathtaking Strip, City & Mountain Views from almost ALL windows. Custom walk-in closet in primary. Expansive loft w/incredible natural light & views from all directions!  VA Assumable Loan at 2.5% Must be VA eligible.
